[0.054162, "o", "\u001b[1;36mACT 1 — WONDER   (~2 min)   The record, and what anyone can do with it.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.054175, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “This is a model I trained. I'm not going to show you the code yet.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.054203, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “I'm going to show you its hash. This model IS this hash.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
